    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I believe that this is how it goes:\n- We're setting the local state with `hitsPerPage: 6`\n- The URL gets updated with `hPP=6`\n- The URL was updated, so the URL sync widget checks if the state of the URL matches the local state\n- It doesn't, since the state from the URL is `hitsPerPage: \"6\"`\n- The local state gets updated with `hitsPerPage: \"6\"`, this triggers a `render` on all widgets\n",
    "created_at": "2015-10-27T13:40:03Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/366#issuecomment-151499781",
